summary: Operations Geologist with a strong background in Petrophysics, demonstrated by a history of working in the oil & energy industry. Providing geological and operational support to different teams with a focus on decommissioning and P&A of wells. Strong research professional skilled in Structural Geology, Stratigraphy, Petrophysics, Cement Evaluations, Geological Mapping, and Earth and Petroleum Science.
